    "body": "### Problem\n\nvim supports easy mode aka `evim`. I see #1656 removed this, however it's a good to have feature. Especially with LSP inbuilt into noevim it can help with easy transition from other editors. I see lot of potential with easy mode for people to experience power of neovim (mainly LSP) without bein overwhelmed with modal editor concepts.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPlease support easy mode with neovim.",
